messages.subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] Things I learned today
messages.msgSnippet: TOO MUCH to learn in one day!
messages.messageBody:
TOO MUCH to learn in one day!

<< That I am quite capable of a temper tantrum :( But kids forgive easily

That if you dehorn a goat, he has big holes in his head all the way down into
his sinuses

That lost sock mates have found a haven behind Zach's toy box

That rabbits only multiply like rabbits if you aren't counting on it for the
stock show :(

That when you're 5, nothing is more fun than riding in the back of a pickup

That sooner or later, kids really do decide to do something other than watch
"Spongebob Squarepants" reruns

That attempting to "firm up" undercooked hard-boiled eggs in the microwave
will cause an explosion
>>

If you peel them first does it help? (The eggs; not the goats, not the kids,
not the poor slow rabbits.)

messages.subject: Things I learned today
messages.msgSnippet: That I am quite capable of a temper tantrum  :(    But kids forgive easily That if you dehorn a goat, he has big holes in his head all the way down into his
messages.messageBody:
That I am quite capable of a temper tantrum :( But kids forgive easily

That if you dehorn a goat, he has big holes in his head all the way down into his sinuses

That lost sock mates have found a haven behind Zach's toy box

That rabbits only multiply like rabbits if you aren't counting on it for the stock show :(

That when you're 5, nothing is more fun than riding in the back of a pickup

That sooner or later, kids really do decide to do something other than watch "Spongebob Squarepants" reruns

That attempting to "firm up" undercooked hard-boiled eggs in the microwave will cause an explosion

Julie

"Give government the weapons to fight your enemy and it will use them against you"--Harry Browne

"They that can give up essential liberty to obtain a little temporary safety deserve neither liberty nor safety"--Benjamin Franklin

"Those who make peaceful revolution impossible will make violent revolution inevitable"-- John F. Kennedy
